@dubeejw 
So there is an issue already open that would address that, Issue #427 .
So I guess we can close this issue and wait for the other to finish

@rabbah In the short term can we at the minimum start by supporting invoking an action with `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` in addition of what we have today `application/json` ?

This will allow Slack commands to work, and any other webhooks that only support `application/x-www-form-urlencoded`

How much effort would this be? In which controller class is the change required?
